text: Ülejõe (Estonian for "Across-the-River") is a neighbourhood of Tartu, Estonia. It has a population of 8,226 (as of 31 December 2013) and an area of . Northern part of Ülejõe was earlier called as Kvissental (:et). ==See also== *University of Tartu Sports Hall *University of Tartu Stadium *Raudsild ==References== Category:Tartu
